        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Markdown-调整图片大小"><a href="#Markdown-调整图片大小" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 调整图片大小"></a>Markdown 调整图片大小</h1><p>Markdown 不能指定图片尺寸，但可以用 HTML 设定宽高：</p><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;/img/eg.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;850&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;450&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/img/eg.png" width="850" height="450"><h1 id="Markdown-图片标题"><a href="#Markdown-图片标题" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 图片标题"></a>Markdown 图片标题</h1><p>Markdown 没有图片标题（Caption），可以使用 HTML 的 &lt;figure&gt; 和 &lt;figcaption&gt;：</p><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">figure</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;img src=&quot;/images/rocks.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;描述文本&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;figcaption&gt;这是一张描述图片。&lt;/figcaption&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/figure&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者使用 Markdown 变通方法：</p><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">描述文本</span>](<span class="link">/img/eg.jpg</span>)  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*这是一张描述图片。*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/eg.png" alt="描述文本"><br><em>异环二测游玩图片。</em></p><h1 id="图床连接性测试"><a href="#图床连接性测试" class="headerlink" title="图床连接性测试"></a>图床连接性测试</h1><p><strong>mjj.today:</strong><br><img src="https://i.miji.bid/2025/06/20/97144fcf45cd0be4c4f96b326f9a9187.png" alt="97144fcf45cd0be4c4f96b326f9a9187.png" border="0" /></p><p><strong>imgloc.com:</strong><br><img src="https://i.imgs.ovh/2025/07/02/kImRr.png" alt="kImRr.png" border="0"></p><p><strong>picui.cn:</strong><br><img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2025/07/02/6864e8e35b1b1.png" alt="Java-runtime-gamma-snapshot Screenshot 2025.06.15 - 15.32.26.27.png" title="Java-runtime-gamma-snapshot Screenshot 2025.06.15 - 15.32.26.27.png" /></p><p><strong>meee.com.tw:</strong><br><img src="https://meee.com.tw/0zW7RPH.gif" border="0" /></p><p><strong>111666.best:</strong><br><img src="https://i.111666.best/image/4tohObX41qCw90K1VPqsyc.jpg" alt="image"></p><hr><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 国际通用</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 部分国内适用</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
